sentences: Yōko Hikasa (日笠 陽子, Hikasa Yōko, born July 16, 1985) is a Japanese voice actress and singer affiliated with I'm Enterprise.
Their first single "Shoot!" was released on August 17, 2011 and was used as the opening theme for the series.
The album Pure Elements was released on October 5, 2011.
